July 27, 2017 2:03 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of The Branford Castle Fund, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Branford Castle Fund, L.P. specializes in investments in buyouts and middle market investments. It prefers to invest in the following sectors: consumer products / services, logistics, value-added commercial distribution, business services, restaurants, manufacturing, materials and medical services. The fund prefers to invest in US and Canada based companies. It typically invests between $5 million and $40 million in companies with enterprise values between $10 million and $75 million; sales values between $10 million and $200 million; and EBITDA between $2 million and $15 million. It prefers to take a majority stake.


