Branford Castle Partners, L.P. Key Developments

Branford Castle Mulls Acquisitions
Feb 27 17
Branford Castle Partners, L.P. is seeking acquisitions. Branford Castle announced its investment Fund has purchased Surface Preparation Technologies, LLC. The transaction follows Branford's recent acquisition of Earthlite Massage Tables. "With this second deal, we are moving efficiently to deploy our investors' capital, and we are working hard to close additional acquisitions in the near future," said John S. Castle, Managing Partner of Branford Castle.


Branford Castle Partners Eyes Acquisitions
Jul 26 16
Branford Castle Partners, L.P. is looking for acquisition opportunities. Branford acquired Earthlite Massage Tables. "Earthlite has established itself as a global leader in the wellness products market with an unparalleled reputation for product quality and innovation," said Laurence Lederer, Managing Director at Branford Castle. "We are excited about this investment and the opportunity to partner with CEO Jim Chenevey and his excellent management team to help them continue to build the business. We believe that the company is poised to grow in its line of tables, and in many other product categories, both through organic growth and through strategic acquisitions."


